---
// WhoWeAre.astro
---

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">
      Why Rebel Ape <span class="text-rebel-green">Is Different</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      We're not your typical marketing agency. We don't hide behind jargon, fake guarantees, or corporate BS. We're the rebels who actually tell you the truth about what works and what doesn't.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
      <img
        src="https://RebelApeCDN.b-cdn.net/featured-4-vital-components-v2.webp"
        alt="Complete marketing systems for roofing contractors"
        class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
      <div class="p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Complete Marketing Systems, Not Random Tactics</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Most agencies sell you a website, or SEO, or Google Ads—then wonder why you're not getting results. We build complete systems where everything works together. Individual tactics fail. Systems generate predictable leads.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
      <img
        src="https://RebelApeCDN.b-cdn.net/featured-roofer-marketing.webp"
        alt="Roofing marketing partners"
        class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
      <div class="p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Marketing Partners, Not Just Another Vendor</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          We're not an agency you pay to run ads while you hope for the best. We own our results. If something's not working, we fix it—together. Most agencies blame your market. We test and optimize until it works.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
      <img
        src="https://RebelApeCDN.b-cdn.net/featured-ai-blogs-contractors.webp"
        alt="Human-driven strategy for contractors"
        class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
      <div class="p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Human-Driven Strategy, Not AI-Regurgitated Content</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          We use AI as a tool, but humans drive the strategy. We don't pump out generic content that works for anyone—we build messaging specifically for your roofing business and your market.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>